nntp2sql (beta .3)

A compact NNTP â†’ SQL ingestor with TLS/STARTTLS, AUTH, multithreaded headers fetch, SQLite/MySQL backends, update-only/upsert DB writes, progress bars, config persistence, and structured logging.

Build:
  cd Isotope
  make nntp2sql        # SQLite default
  make nntp2sql-mysql  # MySQL/MariaDB (set MYSQL_INC/MYSQL_LIB if needed)
  make viewer          # GTK3 viewer (SQLite)

Run:
  ./nntp2sql --host news.example.net --group comp.lang.c --db-type sqlite --db-name headers.db --headers-only
  ./nntp2sql --db-type mariadb --db-name newsdb --init-db --create-db
  ./viewer --sqlite ../headers.db --group comp.lang.c

Docs:
  README.md
  man/nntp2sql.1
